 ng skills in community.  Everyone is welcome\, whether you are an experien
 ced artist or think you cannot draw (spoiler: everyone can draw and everyo
 ne can improve their drawing skills with practice).\nWe’ll open with som
 e time to introduce ourselves to each other and have a brief (optional) wa
 rm-up exercise.  Props will be provided\, but you are also welcome to brin
 g your own.\nIf you are bringing your own supplies\, please bring paper\, 
 pencils\, and anything else you want to use during the session (please no 
 chemicals\, oils\, etc).\n\n\nhttps://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-s1o
 3x-20260112183000
