DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260129T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260129T210000
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an evening of hand embroidery and chit chat. The 
 event is open for experienced embroiderers and those who have never/or sel
 dom picked up a needle. If you’re new to embroidery\, we have a simple
  stitch sampler and supplies that we can use to cover some basic stitches 
 like the running stitch\, back stitch\, chain stitch\, French knots or mak
 e your own sashiko square. If you have questions on a project bring them a
 long\, we’ll try our best to answer them.\n\n\nhttps://bookwhen.com/sequ
 oiafabrica/e/ev-s6b27-20260129190000
LOCATION:1736 18th Street\, San Francisco CA 94107-2343
ORGANIZER:mailto:info@sequoiafabrica.org
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Embroidery Social
URL:https://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-s6b27-20260129190000
END:VEVENT
