BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260320T101640Z
UID:bwnp-x3ixm04f5wj7-ev-sh6ua-20260225180000
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260225T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260225T200000
DESCRIPTION:Have a piece of clothing that isn't getting as much of your att
 ention or love anymore? Have something with imperfections you want to hide
 ? Holes\, rips\, snags\, or tears in your clothing? This is the workshop f
 or you!\nOur instructor has a bunch of fabric samples that would be great 
 for upcycling\, patches and other mending endeavors. We'll have community 
 members there to help you with your projects and instruct or guide you on 
 the best way to complete your goal.\nNote: We will not be completing your 
 projects for you\, we want you to learn how to! This workshop is for peopl
 e who want to be the one mending and sewing (we will help you if it's need
 ed\, of course).\nBring your unloved item and let's transform it into some
 thing you're obsessed with! Fabric and supplies will be provided but feel 
 free to bring your own if you have a project in mind!\n\n\nhttps://bookwhe
 n.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-sh6ua-20260225180000
