DESCRIPTION:Join us to learn the basics of soldering and using a soldering 
 iron. Walk away with a circuit kit you assembled yourself that will do a f
 un little trick\, like flash LEDs\, or respond to light. This is a great c
 hance to learn a new skill with us over at Sequoia Fabrica.\nThis class co
 vers the basics of through-hole soldering\nNotes on the Class\nSoldering p
 erformed properly is a safe\, fun project. We will go over best practices 
 for working with the iron and give you the chance to practice the skill.\n
 \n\nhttps://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-sr0dx-20260305183000
